OL,4,Cstudent fees in NI
OL,6,FStormont's Economy Minister has ruled
OL,7,Fout introducing a significant increase
OL,8,Fto student fees in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FCaoimhe Archibald, who is responsible
OL,11,Ffor higher education funding in the
OL,12,Fregion, made the announcement in
OL,13,Fresponse to a joint call from
OL,14,Funiversities and colleges for a
OL,15,Fsubstantial uplift to the current
OL,16,F#4,750 cap on fees for local students.
