OL,6,FThe heads of Queen's University,
OL,7,FUlster University and the Open
OL,8,FUniversity in Ireland had warned that
OL,9,Ffailure to tackle a funding crisis in
OL,10,Fthe sector would force them to cut
OL,11,Fplaces for local students, as they
OL,12,Finsisted the current arrangements are
OL,13,F"not sustainable".
OL,15,FMs Archibald has now made clear that
OL,16,Fshe will not approve a cap increase
OL,17,Fbeyond the annual inflationary
OL,18,Fadjustment.
