OL,6,FShe said placing an additional
OL,7,Ffinancial burden on students was not
OL,8,Fthe way to address the pressures
OL,9,Ffacing colleges and universities.
OL,11,FThe minister said she would instead
OL,12,Furge other Stormont ministers to
OL,13,Fprioritise the funding of higher
OL,14,Feducation institutions when it comes
OL,15,Fto the reallocation of uncommitted
OL,16,Ffunds during the current financial
OL,17,Fyear. She said a sum of less than #10
OL,18,Fmillion was required this year.
