OL,6,FThe Sinn Fein MLA said she was also
OL,7,Fcommitted to working with the colleges
OL,8,Fand universities to find a sustainable
OL,9,F"longer-term solution" to the funding
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,F"You will be aware that the
OL,13,Funiversities and university colleges
OL,14,Fhave written to the five main parties
OL,15,Fhighlighting the need for additional
OL,16,Ffunding," Ms Archibald told reporters
OL,17,Fat Stormont on Tuesday afternoon.
