OL,6,F"There are two ways to provide that
OL,7,Fadditional funding ` either by
OL,8,Fincreasing student fees above the
OL,9,Fusual level of inflation or by finding
OL,10,Fmore public funding.
OL,12,F"I am clear that the current funding
OL,13,Fmodel does not work for universities
OL,14,Fand it does not work for students.
OL,16,F"And skills are a priority for me and
OL,17,Fmy department in meeting the
OL,18,Fobjectives of my economic vision and
OL,19,Fproviding pathways for people of all
OL,20,Fbackgrounds to gain education and
OL,21,Ftraining.
