OL,6,F"While I recognise the challenges
OL,7,Ffacing universities, I am not prepared
OL,8,Fto raise fees above the usual level of
OL,9,Finflation and push that additional
OL,10,Fpressure onto students.
OL,12,F"I have therefore written to my
OL,13,FExecutive colleagues asking for higher
OL,14,Feducation institutions to be
OL,15,Fprioritised for in-year funding to
OL,16,Faddress the challenges this year.
