OL,6,FIn their letter to party leaders
OL,7,Fearlier this month, the university
OL,8,Fchiefs acknowledged that any increase
OL,9,Fin tuition fees agreed by Stormont
OL,10,Fshould not be seen in "isolation", and
OL,11,Fthey also expressed support for a
OL,12,Fcorresponding rise in the maintenance
OL,13,Fgrant available to students from low-
OL,14,Fincome households.
OL,16,FThe letter was endorsed by the
OL,17,Fprincipals of Northern Ireland's two
OL,18,Fdedicated teacher training colleges,
OL,19,FStranmillis and St Mary's.
