OL,6,FAnnual tuition fees for students from
OL,7,Fthe island of Ireland studying in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland are currently capped
OL,9,Fat #4,750.
OL,11,FStudents from the rest of the UK who
OL,12,Fstudy in Northern Ireland pay up to
OL,13,F#9,250. That is the same amount paid
OL,14,Fby Northern Ireland students studying
OL,15,Fin universities and colleges in
OL,16,FEngland, Scotland and Wales.
OL,18,FThe #9,250 cap is increasing to #9,535
OL,19,Fat the start of the next academic year
OL,20,Fin the autumn.
