OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland university
OL,7,Fleaders were not pressing for major
OL,8,Fstructural changes to the current
OL,9,Ffunding model, rather an increase to
OL,10,Fthe fee cap for island of Ireland
OL,11,Fstudents to reflect the inflationary
OL,12,Fpressures of recent years.
OL,14,FTheir letter expressed frustration
OL,15,Fthat tuition fee increases in Northern
OL,16,FIreland since 2011 have "consistently
OL,17,Ffallen below inflation" while costs
OL,18,Fhave "risen dramatically".
